  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Puttler is a mini-golf puzzle game featuring wacky obstacles and a charming backstory.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/93a21be00e116506cded2db282f9d1dd.poster.avif?t=1752006830\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/93a21be00e116506cded2db282f9d1dd.webm?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/93a21be00e116506cded2db282f9d1dd.mp4?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/382ef8159b7dbf4154cea93ab943f07d.avif?t=1752006830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras_big/382ef8159b7dbf4154cea93ab943f07d.avif?t=1752006830 width=800 height=66 /></span><strong> </strong> <br><strong>The Puttler World Tour has officially begun, and your journey to becoming a professional Puttler starts now! Compete in 14 colorful courses across the globe to build your reputation, earn cash, acquire new Puttlers, and customize your bag. </strong>    <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/3a5b72b5e534e1badd5c046b81e22026.poster.avif?t=1752006830\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/3a5b72b5e534e1badd5c046b81e22026.webm?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/3a5b72b5e534e1badd5c046b81e22026.mp4?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/25eabee85580877d74192521ddce4921.avif?t=1752006830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras_big/25eabee85580877d74192521ddce4921.avif?t=1752006830 width=800 height=66 /></span><strong>Using physics and seven different shapes called \"Puttlers,\" your goal is to sink the golf ball in as few strokes as possible! Build creative solutions to stay under par, or craft complex contraptions to solve each puzzle. </strong>     <br>   <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/304f29398dc2fbceee997e5e46cec67e.poster.avif?t=1752006830\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/304f29398dc2fbceee997e5e46cec67e.webm?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/304f29398dc2fbceee997e5e46cec67e.mp4?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/3127885081dd71beb97b8adc16d71b87.avif?t=1752006830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras_big/3127885081dd71beb97b8adc16d71b87.avif?t=1752006830 width=800 height=66 /></span><strong>➤ 252 satisfying puzzles to solve      </strong>  <br><strong>➤ campaign style progression      </strong> <br><strong>➤ colorful monochromatic graphics     </strong> <br><strong>➤ relaxing ambient nature sounds        </strong> <br><strong>➤ charming backstory and dialogue        </strong> <br><strong>➤ secret bonus course to unlock</strong>  <br>  <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/ea904fdf02fa1f8f88c7d63950e5ac1e.poster.avif?t=1752006830\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/ea904fdf02fa1f8f88c7d63950e5ac1e.webm?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/ea904fdf02fa1f8f88c7d63950e5ac1e.mp4?t=1752006830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras/2d182779f7e413650feb160c6ad178d3.avif?t=1752006830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198680/extras_big/2d182779f7e413650feb160c6ad178d3.avif?t=1752006830 width=800 height=66 /></span><strong>➤ portals       </strong> <br><strong>➤ black holes      </strong> <br><strong>➤ sand pits           </strong> <br><strong>➤ hatches </strong> <br><strong>➤ moving platforms      </strong> <br><strong>➤ fountains </strong><br> <br><strong><u>Developer Note</u></strong>  <br>Hey everyone! My name is Anderson, and I'm the creator of <i>Puttler</i>. If you're considering purchasing my game, please keep in mind that we are a very new indie studio of two friends who poured our hearts into this project. While this game isn't a AAA title with endless workshop content, we still estimate over 30 hours of content to 100% the game. <i>Puttler</i> is meant to be a relaxing and fun puzzle game, so if you end up playing, take your time, create fun solutions, and have fun!🤎</p>",
